{"contents":[{"data":{"text":"我从未见过他们牵手，未见过他们一起欢笑。快乐本身对于他们来说，是属于他们自己的。我一直想，一直以为，他们之间除了争吵从没有过其他。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668058},{"data":{"text":"","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10877184},{"data":{"text":"追溯到我最遥远的记忆，我只记得他带我和小弟去过一次动物园，我已经记不清孔雀开屏的模样了，却真真切切地记得那一次真的开屏了，记得那是一只瘦弱，屏也不全的孔雀。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668060},{"data":{"text":"我忘了当初所有的心情，只有那个残存的孔雀留在我记忆中。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668061},{"data":{"text":"我不知道他有没有拉着我的手，只记得他只陪我看了孔雀。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668062},{"data":{"text":"我儿时所有的记忆从此中断般，我找不到他们的微笑。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668063},{"data":{"text":"","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668064},{"data":{"text":"小三的时候，他们吵着离婚。直到近年母亲才和我说，那是她一辈子最坚决的一次，可是，却被我口口声声的责骂毁了。毁了她的青春，她的幸福。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668065},{"data":{"text":"现在的我一直自责。如果不是我当初的任性，他们会不会好过一点。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668066},{"data":{"text":"","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668067},{"data":{"text":"寒假的时候，再看到他们，两鬓发白。突然觉得时光跑得太快了。我还什么都不会，还什么不能守护的时候，一直以来守护着我们的人，就这样老了。我依然对他百般刁难，就好像看不得他舒坦般，所有的任性刁蛮都用在他身上，因为，只有他们对我不离弃。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668068},{"data":{"text":"","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668069},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":73213,"expandable":true,"height":599,"dimension":"M"},"type":"illus","id":10668253},{"data":{"text":"可是，我却不想离开那里。那个小镇，那些喧嚣自虐的时光，我想守在他们身边。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668070},{"data":{"text":"她却对我说，趁着年轻出去走走吧。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668071},{"data":{"text":"哪个少年不怀着流浪天涯的梦，他们呢，他们走过的地方，走过的痕迹从没有过交集，一场相亲葬送了所有的梦想，被逼搭在一起的道貌岸然伪君子和外强中干伪泼妇，二十几年来，从来没有过欢笑。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668072},{"data":{"text":"","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668073},{"data":{"text":"可是，他们老了。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668074},{"data":{"text":"他们依然像巨人一般包容我的任性妄为，笑着对待我的临近脱逃。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668075},{"data":{"text":"尽管我不是小孩子了。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668076},{"data":{"text":"","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668077},{"data":{"text":"我一直以为，一直坚信我这辈子没办法接受婚姻，可是，他们老了。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668078},{"data":{"text":"除了他们相依相靠还有谁永远在他们身边。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668079},{"data":{"text":"我只想看一次你们真心的笑容，一次便够。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668080},{"data":{"text":"让我相信，其实你们真的可以一起继续走下去的。","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668081},{"data":{"text":"","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":false,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668082},{"data":{"text":"来自 维尼布偶","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":true,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668083},{"data":{"text":"“啊，觉得很意外。另外谢谢给我一个露脸的机会。万年宅腐真的不知道要说什么。每个人心中都有一些不为人知的事情，生活的每一个瞬间都会有所感触。可是，人不该沉溺在自怨自艾中⋯⋯所以，我不知道自己在讲什么。”","format":{"p_indent":false,"p_center":false,"p_quote":true,"p_align":"left","p_bold":false,"t_indent":false}},"type":"paragraph","id":10668084},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"L","seq":73216,"expandable":true,"height":485,"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":10668254}],"title":"他们老了"}